## Blue Nile vs James Allen: Which Should You Use for an Engagement Ring?

Since the Signet merger, Blue Nile and James Allen share significant diamond inventory overlap. Many GIA certificates appear on both platforms simultaneously, often at nearly identical prices. This creates a specific arbitrage opportunity: always cross-reference your chosen GIA report number on both platforms before purchasing.

<table class="dc-custom-table"><thead><tr><th>Factor</th><th>Blue Nile</th><th>James Allen</th><th>Winner</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Natural Diamond Inventory</strong></td><td>160,000+</td><td>120,000+</td><td>Blue Nile</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Lab Diamond Inventory</strong></td><td>128,000+</td><td>90,000+</td><td>Blue Nile</td></tr><tr><td><strong>360° Video Quality</strong></td><td>Standard HD</td><td>Ultra HD + real photo</td><td>James Allen</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Price on Shared GIA #</strong></td><td>Often $10–$80 lower</td><td>Sometimes higher</td><td>Check both always</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Setting Range</strong></td><td>Wide</td><td>Slightly wider custom range</td><td>Tie</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Delivery Speed</strong></td><td>7–12 business days</td><td>7–10 business days</td><td>Tie</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Customer Support</strong></td><td>Chat + phone, strong</td><td>Chat + phone, strong</td><td>Tie</td></tr></tbody></table>

The correct workflow: find your stone on Blue Nile using the proportion filters, note the GIA certificate number, search for the same number on James Allen, compare prices, and buy from whichever is cheaper. On shared inventory this typically saves $10–$80 on sub-$5,000 stones. On a $16,490 2ct, the same GIA number sometimes shows a $150–$300 price difference between platforms.

![Blue Nile vs James Allen merger arbitrage pricing — how Signet's shared diamond inventory creates price discrepancies on same GIA certificates, best strategy for engagement ring buyers 2026](/images/blue-nile-james-allen-sale-banner.avif "Blue Nile vs James Allen Engagement Ring: The Merger Arbitrage Play")

